cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR. 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for denoising distant data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves training models on synthetic data, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of pre-trained embeddings and deep learning models suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. Finally, the paper deals with entity typing, which is a task related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
